title: Dakine Seabreeze 23L Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2014 Seabreeze 23L Pack.
Features: 
- Top flap closure with button magnet
- Interior top drawstring closure
- Vinyl trims
- Adjustable web shoulder straps with vinyl trims
- Metal hardware
- Adjustable vinyl cargo straps to car
